.DT
refresh_worshipper
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
refresh_worshipper

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
refresh_worshipper -  This method deletes the given worshipper by name from all deities' arrays.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void refresh_worshipper(string worshipper)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^worshipper%^RESET%^ - the worshipper to refresh
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if the operation was successful, 0 if it failed

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/deity_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method deletes the given worshipper by name from all
deities' arrays.  This is called by the refresh handler
when the player refreshes or is deleted.
.EP

